cards.Name: Powerline - Taking the Stage
cards.Flavor_Text:
"Goin' to the Powerline concert. Ah! It's unbelievable, man."
-P.J. Pete
cards.Body_Text: Singer 4 (This character counts as cost 4 to sing songs.)

cards.Name: Powerline - World's Greatest Rock Star
cards.Body_Text:
Shift 4 {i} (You may pay 4 {i} to play this on top of one of
your characters named Powerline.)
Singer 9
MASH-UP Once during your turn, whenever this character
sings a song, look at the top 4 cards of your deck. You may
reveal a song card with cost 9 or less and play it for free.
Put the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order.

cards.Name: Mickey Mouse - Brave Little Prince
cards.Body_Text:
Shift 5 {i} (You may pay 5 {i} to play this on top of one of
your characters named Mickey Mouse.)
Evasive (Only characters with Evasive can challenge this
character.)
CROWNING ACHIEVEMENT While this character has a card
under him, he gets +3 {s}, +3 {w}, and +3 {l}.

cards.Name: Max Goof - Rockin' Teen
cards.Body_Text:
Singer 5 (This character counts as cost 5 to
sing songs.)
I JUST WANNA STAY HOME This character can't
move to locations.

cards.Name: Roxanne - Powerline Fan
cards.Body_Text:
CONCERT LOVER: While you have a character with
Singer in play, this character gets +1 {s} and +1 {l}.

cards.Name: P.J. Pete - Caught Up in the Music
cards.Flavor_Text: He's a real music buff.
cards.Body_Text:
SHOUT OUT LOUD!: Whenever you play a song, this
character gets +2 {s} this turn.

cards.Name: Gaston - Arrogant Hunter
cards.Flavor_Text: It's not arrogance when you really are the best.
cards.Body_Text:
Reckless (This character can't quest and must
challenge each turn if able.)

cards.Name: Moana - Undeterred Voyager
cards.Flavor_Text: No fire or storm will keep her from her goal.
cards.Body_Text:
Evasive (Only characters with Evasive can
challenge this character.)

cards.Name: Powerline - Musical Superstar
cards.Flavor_Text: "For the first time ever, we're seeing it eye to eye."
cards.Body_Text:
ELECTRIC MOVE: If you've played a song this turn,
this character gains Rush this turn. (They can
challenge the turn they're played.)

cards.Name: Sisu - Emboldened Warrior
cards.Flavor_Text:
Sometimes the only way to fight the unimaginable
is with the incredible.
cards.Body_Text:
SURGE OF POWER: This character gets +1 {s} for
each card in opponents' hands.

cards.Name: Sisu - Daring Visitor
cards.Flavor_Text: "Come on-what's the worst that can happen?"
cards.Body_Text:
Evasive (Only characters with Evasive can challenge
this character.)
BRING ON THE HEAT! When you play this character,
banish chosen opposing character with 1 {s} or less.

cards.Name: Queen of Hearts - Sensing Weakness
cards.Body_Text:
Shift 2 {i} (You may pay 2 {i} to play this on top of
one of your characters named Queen of Hearts.)
LET THE GAME BEGIN Whenever one of your
characters challenges another character, you may
draw a card.

cards.Name: Lumiere - Fiery Friend
cards.Flavor_Text:
"The invaders are at our gates, mes amis! It's time to
show them what we're made of."
cards.Body_Text: FERVENT ADDRESS: Your other characters get +1 {s}.

cards.Name: Card Soldiers - Full Deck
cards.Flavor_Text: You'll have to deal with them sooner or later.

cards.Name: Queen of Hearts - Impulsive Ruler
cards.Flavor_Text:
The glow of lore in the flood caught her eye.
"The spellbook!" she cried. "Don't let it get away!"
cards.Body_Text:
Rush (This character can challenge the turn
they're played.)

cards.Name: Rapunzel - Letting Down Her Hair
cards.Flavor_Text: "Who are you? And how did you find me?"
cards.Body_Text:
TANGLE: When you play this character, each
opponent loses 1 lore.

cards.Name: Mulan - Injured Soldier
cards.Flavor_Text: She'll never give up.
cards.Body_Text:
BATTLE WOUND: This character enters play with
2 damage.

cards.Name: Mulan - Elite Archer
cards.Body_Text:
Shift 5 {i} (You may pay 5 {i} to play this on top of one of your
characters named Mulan.)
STRAIGHT SHOOTER When you play this character, if you
used Shift to play her, she gets +3 {s} this turn.
TRIPLE SHOT During your turn, whenever this character
deals damage to another character in a challenge, deal the
same amount of damage to up to 2 other chosen characters.

cards.Name: Raya - Headstrong
cards.Flavor_Text:
Two parts bravery, one part cleverness, and a whole
lot of determination.
cards.Body_Text:
NOTE TO SELF, DON'T DIE: During your turn, whenever
this character banishes another character in a
challenge, you may ready this character. If you do,
she can't quest for the rest of this turn.

cards.Name: Sergeant Tibbs - Courageous Cat
cards.Flavor_Text: "Yes, sir. Righto, sir. Right away, sir!"

cards.Name: Tuk Tuk - Lively Partner
cards.Body_Text:
Evasive (Only characters with Evasive can challenge this
character.)
ON A ROLL When you play this character, you may
move him and one of your other characters to the
same location for free. If you do, the other character
gets +2 {s} this turn.

cards.Name: I2I
cards.Body_Text:
Sing Together 9 (Any number of your or your teammates'
characters with total cost 9 or more may {e} to sing this song
for free.)
Each player draws 2 cards and gains 2 lore. If 2 or more
characters sang this song, ready them. They can't quest for
the rest of this turn.

cards.Name: You Can Fly!
cards.Body_Text:
(A character with cost 2 or more can {e} to sing this
song for free.)
Chosen character gains Evasive until the start of
your next turn. (Only characters with Evasive can
challenge them.)

cards.Name: A Pirate's Life
cards.Flavor_Text:
Give me a career
As a buccaneer
cards.Body_Text:
Sing Together 6 (Any number of your or your teammates'
characters with total cost 6 or more may {e} to sing this song
for free.)
Each opponent loses 2 lore. You gain 2 lore.

cards.Name: Be King Undisputed
cards.Flavor_Text: Respected, saluted
cards.Body_Text:
(A character with cost 4 or more can {e} to sing this
song for free.)
Each opponent chooses and banishes one of their
characters.

cards.Name: Medallion Weights
cards.Body_Text:
DISCIPLINE AND STRENGTH: {e}, 2 {i} - Chosen
character gets +2 {s} this turn. Whenever they
challenge another character this turn, you may
draw a card.

cards.Name: Dinner Bell
cards.Flavor_Text: The delicate sound of impending doom.
cards.Body_Text:
YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENS: {e}, 2 {i} - Draw cards
equal to the damage on chosen character of yours,
then banish them.

cards.Name: Agrabah - Marketplace
cards.Flavor_Text:
"Welcome to Agrabah, city of mystery, of enchantment, and the finest merchandise this
side of the river."
-Merchant

cards.Name: Anna - True-Hearted
cards.Flavor_Text:
Make sure you know what's truly important and be
willing to fight for it.

cards.Name: Huey - Savvy Nephew
cards.Flavor_Text: "This looks like part of a larger crystal!"
cards.Body_Text:
Support (Whenever this character quests, you may add
their {s} to another chosen character's {s} this turn.)
THREE NEPHEWS Whenever this character quests, if you
have characters named Dewey and Louie in play, you
may draw 3 cards.

cards.Name: Dewey - Showy Nephew
cards.Flavor_Text: "I got it! I knew I could do it! Dewey for the win!"
cards.Body_Text:
Support (Whenever this character quests, you
may add their {s} to another chosen character's
{s} this turn.)

cards.Name: Louie - Chill Nephew
cards.Flavor_Text: "Found the last one!"
cards.Body_Text:
Support (Whenever this character quests, you
may add their {s} to another chosen character's
{s} this turn.)

cards.Name: Alice - Accidentally Adrift
cards.Body_Text:
WASHED AWAY: When you play this character,
you may put chosen item into its player's inkwell
facedown and exerted.
MAKING WAVES Whenever this character quests,
chosen opposing character gets -2 {s} this turn.

cards.Name: Mulan - Considerate Diplomat
cards.Body_Text:
IMPERIAL INVITATION: Whenever this character
quests, look at the top 4 cards of your deck. You
may reveal a Princess character card and put it
into your hand. Put the rest on the bottom of your
deck in any order.

cards.Name: Cruella De Vil - Style Icon
cards.Body_Text:
OUT OF SEASON: Once during your turn, whenever
a character with cost 2 or less is banished, put the
top card of your deck into your inkwell facedown
and exerted.
INSULTING REMARK During your turn, each opposing
character with cost 2 or less gets -1 {s}.

cards.Name: Mufasa - King of the Pride Lands
cards.Flavor_Text:
"A king must care for all of the creatures in his
kingdom, no matter their size."

cards.Name: Cruella De Vil - Fashionable Cruiser
cards.Flavor_Text:
"Isn't it just gorgeous, darling? And just as stylish
as I am."
cards.Body_Text:
NOW GET GOING: During your turn, this character
gains Evasive. (They can challenge characters
with Evasive.)

cards.Name: Anna - Braving the Storm
cards.Flavor_Text:
After talking to Olaf, Anna marched into the
unexpected storm to save Kristoff.
cards.Body_Text:
I WAS BORN READY While you have another Hero
character in play, this character gets +1 {l}.

cards.Name: Flounder - Voice of Reason
cards.Flavor_Text:
"Excitement...adventure...danger lurking
around every cor- AAAAAGGH!"

cards.Name: Hans - Noble Scoundrel
cards.Flavor_Text:
Hans was confident he could bring Anna to Ursula-
all he needed was something of Kristoff's to lure her in.
cards.Body_Text:
ROYAL SCHEMES: When you play this character, if a
Princess or Queen character is in play, gain 1 lore.

cards.Name: The Queen - Mirror Seeker
cards.Flavor_Text:
She has only one question, and she'd better like
the answer.
cards.Body_Text:
CALCULATING AND VAIN: Whenever this character
quests, you may look at the top 3 cards of your
deck and put them back in any order.

cards.Name: Grand Pabbie - Oldest and Wisest
cards.Flavor_Text: When he talks, even the sky listens.
cards.Body_Text:
ANCIENT INSIGHT: Whenever you remove 1 or
more damage from one of your characters,
gain 2 lore.

cards.Name: Hades - Infernal Schemer
cards.Flavor_Text:
"He's gotta have a weakness, because everybody's
got a weakness."
cards.Body_Text:
IS THERE A DOWNSIDE TO THIS?: When you play
this character, you may put chosen opposing
character into their player's inkwell facedown.

cards.Name: Mama Odie - Mystical Maven
cards.Flavor_Text: "You dig a little deeper, you'll find everything you need."
cards.Body_Text:
THIS GOING TO BE GOOD: Whenever you play a song,
you may put the top card of your deck into your inkwell
facedown and exerted.

cards.Name: Aurora - Dreaming Guardian
cards.Flavor_Text: As the princess slumbered, her power awoke.
cards.Body_Text:
Shift 3 {i} (You may pay 3 {i} to play this on top of one of
your characters named Aurora.)
PROTECTIVE EMBRACE Your other characters gain Ward.
(Opponents can't choose them except to challenge.)

cards.Name: Aurora - Tranquil Princess
cards.Flavor_Text:
Her music fills the Illuminary's gardens with joy
and light.
cards.Body_Text:
Ward (Opponents can't choose this character
except to challenge.)

cards.Name: Jasmine - Heir of Agrabah
cards.Flavor_Text:
She may be young, but she's got the spirit of a
true leader.
cards.Body_Text:
I'M A FAST LEARNER When you play this character,
remove up to 1 damage from chosen character
of yours.

cards.Name: Belle - Inventive Engineer
cards.Flavor_Text:
A little ingenuity and a lot of heart will take you far
in this world.
cards.Body_Text:
TINKER: Whenever this character quests, you pay
1 {i} less for the next item you play this turn.

cards.Name: Judy Hopps - Optimistic Officer
cards.Flavor_Text:
"I'll get to the bottom of what happened with the
locked lorebook. You can count on me!"
cards.Body_Text:
DON'T CALL ME CUTE: When you play this
character, you may banish chosen item. If you do,
its player draws a card.

cards.Name: Maid Marian - Delightful Dreamer
cards.Flavor_Text: She makes every space more beautiful.
cards.Body_Text:
HIGHBORN LADY: When you play this character,
chosen character gets -2 {s} this turn.

cards.Name: Winnie the Pooh - Having a Think
cards.Flavor_Text:
When he thought, he thought in the most
thoughtful way he could think.
cards.Body_Text:
HUNNY POT: Whenever this character quests,
you may put a card from your hand into your
inkwell facedown.

cards.Name: Alice - Growing Girl
cards.Body_Text:
GOOD ADVICE: Your other characters gain
Support. (Whenever they quest, you may add their
{s} to another chosen character's {s} this turn.)
WHAT DID I DO? While this character has 10 {s}
or more, she gets +4 {l}.

cards.Name: Aurora - Regal Princess
cards.Flavor_Text:
"They say if you dream a thing more than once,
it's sure to come true!"

cards.Name: Robin Hood - Unrivaled Archer
cards.Flavor_Text:
"We never rob. We just sort of borrow a bit from those who
can afford it."
cards.Body_Text:
FEED THE POOR: When you play this character, if an
opponent has more cards in their hand than you, you may
draw a card.
GOOD SHOT During your turn, this character gains Evasive.
(They can challenge characters with Evasive.)

cards.Name: Develop Your Brain
cards.Flavor_Text:
"Knowledge, wisdom-there's the real power!"
-Merlin
cards.Body_Text:
Look at the top 2 cards of your deck. Put one into your
hand and the other on the bottom of your deck.

cards.Name: Four Dozen Eggs
cards.Body_Text:
(A character with cost 4 or more can {e} to sing this
song for free.)
Your characters gain Resist +2 until the start of your
next turn. (Damage dealt to them is reduced by 2.)

cards.Name: One Jump Ahead
cards.Flavor_Text:
Gotta eat to live, gotta steal to eat-
Tell you all about it when I got the time
cards.Body_Text:
(A character with cost 2 or more can {e} to sing this song
for free.)
Put the top card of your deck into your inkwell facedown
and exerted.

cards.Name: Dig a Little Deeper
cards.Body_Text:
Sing Together 8 (Any number of your or your teammates'
characters with total cost 8 or more may {e} to sing this
song for free.)
Look at the top 7 cards of your deck. Put 2 into your hand
and the rest on the bottom of your deck in any order.

cards.Name: Aurelian Gyrosensor
cards.Flavor_Text:
"It can point you toward lost lore, but if you're not careful,
it'll lead you off a cliff."
-Venturo, an Illumineer
cards.Body_Text:
SEEKING KNOWLEDGE: Whenever one of your characters
quests, you may look at the top card of your deck. Put it
on either the top or the bottom of your deck.

cards.Name: Heart of Te Fiti
cards.Flavor_Text: It takes a pure heart to calm the raging storm within.
cards.Body_Text:
CREATE LIFE: {e}, 2 {i} - Put the top card of your deck
into your inkwell facedown and exerted.

cards.Name: Coconut Basket
cards.Flavor_Text:
The coconut is a versatile gift from the gods, used to make
nearly everything-including baskets to carry more coconuts.
cards.Body_Text:
CONSIDER THE COCONUT: Whenever you play a character, you
may remove up to 2 damage from chosen character.

cards.Name: Motunui - Island Paradise
cards.Body_Text:
REINCARNATION: Whenever a character is banished while here, you may
put that card into your inkwell facedown and exerted.

cards.Name: Philoctetes - No-Nonsense Instructor
cards.Body_Text:
YOU GOTTA STAY FOCUSED: Your Hero characters
gain Challenger +1. (They get +1 {s} while
challenging.)
SHAMELESS PROMOTER Whenever you play a
Hero character, gain 1 lore.

cards.Name: Mickey Mouse - Trumpeter
cards.Body_Text: SOUND THE CALL: {e}, 2 {i} - Play a character for free.

cards.Name: Nala - Undaunted Lioness
cards.Body_Text:
DETERMINED DIVERSION: While this character has
no damage, she gets +1 {l} and gains Resist +1.
(Damage dealt to them is reduced by 1.)

cards.Name: Lilo - Best Explorer Ever
cards.Body_Text:
COME ON, PEOPLE, LET'S MOVE: When you play this
character, your other characters gain Challenger +2 this
turn. (They get +2 {s} while challenging.)
GO GET 'EM Whenever this character quests, chosen
Alien character gains Challenger +2 and "This character
can challenge ready characters" this turn.

cards.Name: Scar - Finally King
cards.Body_Text:
BE GRATEFUL: Your Ally characters get +1 {s}.
STICK WITH ME At the end of your turn, if this character
is exerted, you may draw cards equal to the {s} of
chosen Ally character of yours. If you do, choose and
discard 2 cards and banish that character.

cards.Name: Little John - Sir Reginald
cards.Body_Text:
WHAT A BEAUTIFUL BRAWL!: When you play this
character, choose one:
- Chosen Hero character gains Resist +2 this turn.
(Damage dealt to them is reduced by 2.)
- Deal 2 damage to chosen Villain character.

cards.Name: Robin Hood - Champion of Sherwood
cards.Body_Text:
Shift 3 {i} (You may pay 3 {i} to play this on top of one of your
characters named Robin Hood.)
SKILLED COMBATANT During your turn, whenever this
character banishes another character in a challenge, gain 2 lore.
THE GOOD OF OTHERS When this character is banished in a
challenge, you may draw a card.

cards.Name: Jasmine - Fearless Princess
Tiana - Diligent Waitress
cards.Flavor_Text:
"My place is going to be special, with great food
to fill people's bellies and hot jazz to feed their
souls!"

cards.Name: Benja - Guardian of the Dragon Gem
cards.Flavor_Text: "Don't mistake spirit for skill."
cards.Body_Text:
WE HAVE A CHOICE: When you play this character,
you may banish chosen item.

cards.Name: Jafar - Royal Vizier
cards.Flavor_Text: "Soon you'll learn who holds the real power!"
cards.Body_Text:
I DON'T TRUST HIM, SIRE During your turn, this
character gains Evasive. (They can challenge
characters with Evasive.)

cards.Name: Prince Naveen - Penniless Royal
cards.Flavor_Text: All he's got is his charm.

cards.Name: Eeyore - Overstuffed Donkey
cards.Flavor_Text: "Not much of a roadblock, but I suppose I'll do."
cards.Body_Text:
Resist +1 (Damage dealt to this character is
reduced by 1.)

cards.Name: Robin Hood - Capable Fighter
cards.Flavor_Text:
"Capable? You don't know the half of it."
-Little John
cards.Body_Text:
SKIRMISH: {e} - Deal 1 damage to chosen
character.

cards.Name: Mickey Mouse - Standard Bearer
cards.Flavor_Text:
He sets the standard for intrepid adventurers
everywhere.
cards.Body_Text:
STAND STRONG: When you play this character,
chosen character gains Challenger +2 this turn.
(They get +2 {s} while challenging.)

cards.Name: Hercules - Beloved Hero
cards.Body_Text:
Bodyguard (This character may enter play exerted.
An opposing character who challenges one of your
characters must choose one with Bodyguard if able.)
Resist +1 (Damage dealt to this character is
reduced by 1.)

cards.Name: Lawrence - Jealous Manservant
cards.Flavor_Text: In this new world, the crown could finally be his.
cards.Body_Text:
PAYBACK: While this character has no damage,
he gets +4 {s}.

cards.Name: Tinker Bell - Giant Fairy
cards.Body_Text:
Shift 4 {i} (You may pay 4 {i} to play this on top of one of
your characters named Tinker Bell.)
ROCK THE BOAT When you play this character, deal 1
damage to each opposing character.
PUNY PIRATE! During your turn, whenever this character
banishes another character in a challenge, you may deal 2
damage to chosen opposing character.

cards.Name: Tinker Bell - Tiny Tactician
cards.Flavor_Text: Sometimes all you need is a little tactical genius.
cards.Body_Text:
BATTLE PLANS: {e} - Draw a card, then choose and
discard a card.

cards.Name: Captain Hook - Captain of the Jolly Roger
cards.Flavor_Text:
"A pretty sight, Mr. Smee. We'll pot 'em like sitting
ducks."
cards.Body_Text:
DOUBLE THE POWDER!: When you play this
character, you may return an action card named
Fire the Cannons! from your discard to your hand.

cards.Name: Hercules - True Hero
cards.Flavor_Text: "You gotta admit, that was pretty heroic."
cards.Body_Text:
Bodyguard (This character may enter play exerted.
An opposing character who challenges one of
your characters must choose one with Bodyguard
if able.)

cards.Name: John Silver - Greedy Treasure Seeker
cards.Flavor_Text:
The eighth Rule of Villainy: Don't underestimate the
power of a bad reputation.
cards.Body_Text:
CHART YOUR OWN COURSE: For each location you have
in play, this character gains Resist +1 and gets +1 {l}.
(Damage dealt to them is reduced by 1.)

cards.Name: Li Shang - Imperial Captain
cards.Flavor_Text:
Immovable as a mountain and fierce as a dragon-
the Empire's finest warrior.

cards.Name: Prince Eric - Dashing and Brave
cards.Flavor_Text: "I lost her once! I'm not gonna lose her again!"
cards.Body_Text:
Challenger +2 (While challenging, this character
gets +2 {s}.)

cards.Name: Ariel - Sonic Warrior
cards.Body_Text:
Shift 4 {i} (You may pay 4 {i} to play this on top of
one of your characters named Ariel.)
AMPLIFIED VOICE Whenever you play a song,
you may pay 2 {i} to deal 3 damage to chosen
character.

cards.Name: Ariel - Determined Mermaid
cards.Flavor_Text: Everything she's ever wanted is almost in reach.
cards.Body_Text:
I WANT MORE Whenever you play a song, you
may draw a card, then choose and discard a card.

cards.Name: One Last Hope
cards.Body_Text:
(A character with cost 3 or more can {e} to sing this
song for free.)
Chosen character gains Resist +2 until the start of your
next turn. If a Hero character is chosen, they can also
challenge ready characters this turn. (Damage dealt to
them is reduced by 2.)

cards.Name: Smash
cards.Flavor_Text: "Go away!"
cards.Body_Text: Deal 3 damage to chosen character.

cards.Name: I Find 'Em, I Flatten 'Em
cards.Flavor_Text:
I don't ask how hard the work is
Got a rough, indestructible surface
cards.Body_Text:
(A character with cost 4 or more can {e} to sing this
song for free.)
Banish all items.

cards.Name: Fire the Cannons!
cards.Flavor_Text:
Captain Hook: "Double the powder and shorten the
fuse!"
Mr. Smee: "Shorten the powder and double the fuse!"
cards.Body_Text: Deal 2 damage to chosen character.

cards.Name: Strength of a Raging Fire
cards.Flavor_Text:
Tranquil as a forest
But on fire within
cards.Body_Text:
(A character with cost 3 or more can {e} to sing this song
for free.)
Deal damage to chosen character equal to the number of
characters you have in play.

cards.Name: The Mob Song
cards.Body_Text:
Sing Together 10 (Any number of your or your
teammates' characters with total cost 10 or more may
{e} to sing this song for free.)
Deal 3 damage to up to 3 chosen characters and/or
locations.

cards.Name: Beast's Mirror
cards.Flavor_Text:
Ashamed of his monstrous form, the Beast concealed
himself inside his castle, with a magic mirror as his only
window to the outside world.
cards.Body_Text:
SHOW ME: {e}, 3 {i} - If you have no cards in your hand,
draw a card.

cards.Name: Maui's Place of Exile - Hidden Island
cards.Flavor_Text: Nothing but boulders and sand-easy to miss.
cards.Body_Text:
ISOLATED: Characters gain Resist +1 while here. (Damage dealt to them
is reduced by 1.)
